		<p style="color:black; font-size: 150%; text-align: center;">
		<br>
		Welcome! We are a local specialty coffee shop offering single-origin coffee, 
		a rotating selection of pourovers, nitro cold brew on tap, and locally made 
		loose-leaf tea. Our owner has been working in the coffee industry for the last 15 
		years, and it has always been her dream to open a place of her own. We are 
		thrilled to bring Sap Coffee Company to the place we call home : Waterbury, 
		Vermont! We created Sap Coffee Company because some of our favorite memories 
		are spent exploring in the mountains with a great cup of coffee. To us, coffee is rustic, 
		full of adventure, and is best when tasting with friends and family. It is our 
		pleasure to share our love in crafting coffee, and without your support we 
		simply wouldn't be here! We thank you for visiting us, and can't wait to welcome you back.
